@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Add Customer

|Sales User|
start
:Open "Add Customer" form;
:Fill in customer data;
:Click "Save";

|CRM System|
:Receive POST /customers/add;
:Validate input;

if (Input valid?) then (Yes)
  :Create customer record;
  :Flash success message;
  :Redirect to /customers;
  :Render customers list;
  stop
else (No)
  :Flash error message;
  :Redirect back to /customers/add;
  |Sales User|
  :Correct input;
  --> :Click "Save";
endif

@enduml